{"tid":238531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"站係資源運用立場，屌人偽善既人係咪貢獻最少？","createTime":"2017-05-11T05:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T08:43:31.000Z","uid":31773,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd41113ec828cfe6c9d99c00fd17f2178341caf0","tid":238531,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"先不論背後意圖或目的，偽善者最起碼有做出所謂善舉作出貢獻，而贏取道德光環。<br />\n<br />\n而批評者往往基於其立場出發，係唔會做出所謂偽善之善舉，如果做出則有違其立場，以捐肝新聞為例，批評捐肝者此行偽善，故他們不會仿效;不論捐肝成效如何，捐肝者最起碼有所貢獻，令社會資源有效分配<br />\n<br />\n而站係道德立場，屌人偽善 者往往自稱其自身無道德可言，但往往站係道德高地，以一個高標準批評偽善者，頗為自相矛盾。"},{"pid":"889c3c79f34fa819886d5a4836cc2912af75cbb5","tid":238531,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d5067e708b6be2d6679679cff3f8ae81f0055f","tid":238531,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"認同, 善事應該係睇結果, 唔係批判動機"},{"pid":"3f2a49c4fd66c7f927e38ff607def698de33444a","tid":238531,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同, 善事應該係睇結果, 唔係批判動機</blockquote><br />\n反而最偽善可能係批評個班，因為拎住左道德既矛頭去周圍攻擊"},{"pid":"b8065b7be0950eaa8f706834d2650e340c6967e1","tid":238531,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a749df0c1c2508403cff911b419be63d0beca7","tid":238531,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05dc5654dd91f15554a44c6ef637f2c670f81458","tid":238531,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎討論"}]}